            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 md:space-x-6">
                <span class="text-sm md:text-body text-grey">06</span>
                <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 text-grey opacity-50 group-hover:text-black group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all">
                  Siz isteyin biz tasarlayalım
